WITH ranked_nations AS (
    SELECT n.n_name, n.n_regionkey, COUNT(s.s_suppkey) AS supplier_count
    FROM nation n
    JOIN supplier s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
    GROUP BY n.n_name, n.n_regionkey
),
total_parts AS (
    SELECT ps.ps_suppkey, SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available
    FROM partsupp ps
    GROUP BY ps.ps_suppkey
),
order_summary AS (
    SELECT c.c_custkey, c.c_name, SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS customer_total
    FROM customer c
    JOIN orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
    GROUP BY c.c_custkey, c.c_name
)
SELECT rn.n_name AS nation_name,
       COUNT(DISTINCT os.c_custkey) AS total_customers,
       SUM(tp.total_available) AS total_parts_available,
       AVG(os.customer_total) AS avg_customer_spending
FROM ranked_nations rn
JOIN total_parts tp ON rn.supplier_count > 10
JOIN order_summary os ON rn.n_regionkey = (SELECT r.r_regionkey FROM region r WHERE r.r_name = 'Asia')
WHERE rn.supplier_count IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY rn.n_name
ORDER BY total_customers DESC, avg_customer_spending DESC
LIMIT 10

SELECT COALESCE("c_custkey", "c_custkey") AS "c_custkey", "c_name", "c_address", "c_nationkey", "c_phone", "c_acctbal", "c_mktsegment", "c_comment"
FROM "customer"

SELECT COALESCE("t13"."NATION_NAME", "t13"."NATION_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", "t13"."TOTAL_CUSTOMERS", "t13"."TOTAL_PARTS_AVAILABLE", "t13"."AVG_CUSTOMER_SPENDING"
FROM (SELECT MIN("t5"."N_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "t7"."C_CUSTKEY") AS "TOTAL_CUSTOMERS", SUM("t5"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE") AS "TOTAL_PARTS_AVAILABLE", AVG("t7"."CUSTOMER_TOTAL") AS "AVG_CUSTOMER_SPENDING"
FROM (SELECT "t2"."N_NAME", "t2"."N_REGIONKEY", "t2"."SUPPLIER_COUNT", "t4"."PS_SUPPKEY", "t4"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE"
FROM (SELECT "nation"."n_name" AS "N_NAME", "nation"."n_regionkey" AS "N_REGIONKEY", COUNT(*) AS "SUPPLIER_COUNT", COUNT(*) > 10 AS "FD_D_f3"

INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier"."s_nationkey"
GROUP BY "nation"."n_name", "nation"."n_regionkey") AS "t2"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "ps_suppkey" AS "PS_SUPPKEY", SUM("ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE"
FROM "partsupp"
GROUP BY "ps_suppkey") AS "t4" ON "t2"."FD_D_f3") AS "t5"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "s1"."c_custkey" AS "C_CUSTKEY", "s1"."c_name" AS "C_NAME", SUM("orders"."o_totalprice") AS "CUSTOMER_TOTAL"
FROM "s1"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "s1"."c_custkey" = "orders"."o_custkey"

FROM "region"
WHERE "r_name" = 'Asia')))
GROUP BY "t5"."N_NAME"
ORDER BY 2 DESC NULLS FIRST, 4 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t13"
